### Hadith 3:190

*Narrated 'Aisha:*

Allah's Apostle used to fast till one would say that he would never stop
fasting, and he would abandon fasting till one would say that he would
never fast. I never saw Allah's Apostle fasting for a whole month except
the month of Ramadan, and did not see him fasting in any month more than
in the month of Sha'ban.

